Text: REPST Busy are you I suspected as much Tuesday is fine where Have you had your garage sale yet Cheers Original Message From mailto Sent Monday August AM To Greenall Geri Subject RE Sorry I was out Friday Hows about comin out for a beer Tuesday with the whole gang If your uncomfortable with hangin out with a bunch of Enron people then maybe we can catch a QUICK one tonight Cheers Original
